        <Summary>pyinotify is a Python module for watching filesystems changes</Summary>
        <Description>pyinotify is a Python module for watching filesystems changes. pyinotify can be used for various kind of fs monitoring. pyinotify relies on a recent Linux Kernel feature (merged in kernel 2.6.13) called inotify. inotify is an event-driven notifier, its notifications are exported from kernel space to user space. </Description>
